{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_bg.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_06.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_06.png","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_10.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20191.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day10.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh...hey there."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Today's the day that a Witch appears@at the shopping mall, isn't it?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Miss Miki got injured there before..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Are you going to let it happen again?"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Last time, I had to prioritize@protecting Madoka."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-7"},{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If we can avoid the need for that,@it's a different story."},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh, good... So, Miss Miki won't have@to end up in the hospital again."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200902}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-9"},{"id":200902,"voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I underestimated Madoka before."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-10"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I thought she would be scared off@if she learned the dangers..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But her friend getting hurt only@pushed her closer to making a contract."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]This time, we'll see to it that they@never cross paths with the Witch."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That does sound like a better solution."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]There is one problem, though. Another@Witch also appears at the same time."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh, right...@I remember you mentioning that."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Last time, didn't you have@Mami Tomoe handle one of them?"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-17"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]This time around, I sent her off@to handle another town."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-18"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Having her jump in while we're hunting@Witches, like in the last loop, is risky."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's true... The fewer wild cards,@the better, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But then...how should we handle this...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20][chara:200902:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...Ah!"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]D-don't tell me...you expect me to@take on one of the Witches by myself?!"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-23"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You'll be fine."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-24"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20][chara:200902:effect_shake]No way, no way, NO WAY!@I can't defeat a Witch all on my own!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Don't you remember how I failed@last time?!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-26"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I was just kidding."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-27"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I thought so!@THANK GOODNESS!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-28"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Seriously, Miss Akemi... Could you stop@telling jokes with such a straight face?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-29"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If you'd use your head a little,@you'd see how obvious it is."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-30"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Kyubey is going to try and make contact@with Madoka during the Witch encounters."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-31"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So you need to remain by Madoka's side."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-32"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well, I get that part..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-33"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'll quickly deal with the Witch on the@school path, then head to the mall."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-34"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]While I'm doing that,@I'll need you to keep stalling."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-35"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Stalling, as in...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-36"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Keeping Madoka and Sayaka Miki as@far away from the Witch as possible."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-37"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm counting on you."},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-38"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Sure, got it. Handling something@like that should be no biggie."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200902}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906110-035-38"}]},"version":3}
